nder Weapon Hardpoints | 4 Capital Weapon Hardpoints | 4 Large Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Capital Missile Bay | 1 Capital Drone Port Module | 8 Turret Gunners\n2392\n0,072 FP/$\nBUSAN MAIDEN HEART\nLegendary Capital Fighter\n4 Capital Weapon Hardpoints | 4 Large Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Capital Missile Bay | 1 Capital Drone Port Module | 6 Turret Gunners\n1344\n0,041 FP/$\nCALICO GUARDIAN\nLegendary Capital Multi-Role\n5 Capital Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Capital Missile Bay | 1 Large Drone Port Module | 5 Turret Gunners\n1158\n0,038 FP/$\nOGRIKA JOD ASTERIS\nLegendary Capital Transport\n4 Capital Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Capital Missile Bay | 3 Turret Gunners\n949\n0,031 FP/$\nFIMBUL ECOS BOMBARELLA\nLegendary Capital Bomber\n4 Large Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Capital Missile Bay | 1 Capital Ammunition Module | 4 Turret Gunners\n730\n0,020 FP/$\nPEARCE D9\nLegendary Capital Salvage\n14 Medium Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Capital Missile Bay | 1 Capital Drone Port Module\n654\n0,022 FP/$\nFIMBUL ECOS GREENADER\nEpic Large Bomber\n6 Medium Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Capital Missile Bay | 1 Large Ammunition Module | 2 Turret Gunners\n610\n0,071 FP/$\nOGRIKA THRIPID\nLegendary Large Fighter\n4 Large Weapon Hardpoints | 2 Large Missile Bays | 1 Large Ammunition Module | 2 Turret Gunners\n564\n0,066 FP/$\nOPAL BITBOAT\nEpic Large Transport\n4 Large Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Large Missile Bay\n406\n0,038 FP/$\nCALICO ENFORCER\nUncommon Medium Fighter\n1 Capital Weapon Hardpoints | 2 Medium Weapon Hardpoints | 2 Medium Missile Bays | 1 Medium Ammunition Module\n364\n0,150 FP/$\nRAINBOW ARC\nEpic Large Freighter\n4 Large Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Medium Missile Bay\n319\n0,023 FP/$\nPEARCE F4\nRare Medium Fighter\n2 Large Weapon Hardpoints | 2 Medium Missile Bays | 1 Turret Gunner\n268\n0,094 FP/$\nPEARCE R8\nEpic Large Refuel / Repair\n2 Large Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Large Missile Bay\n258\n0,023 FP/$\nFIMBUL MAMBA\nUncommon Medium Bounty Hunter\n2 Large Weapon Hardpoints | 2 Medium Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Medium Missile Bay | 1 Small Ammunition Module | 1 Turret Gunner\n234\n0,125 FP/$\nOGRIKA SUNPAA\nEpic Large Freighter\n4 Medium Weapon Hardpoints | 2 Medium Missile Bays\n194\n0,020 FP/$\nCALICO COMPAKT HERO\nRare Medium Multi-Role\n4 Medium Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Medium Missile Bay\n162\n0,043 FP/$\nOGRIKA TURSIC\nEpic Medium Fighter\n4 Medium Weapon Hardpoints | 2 Small Missile Bays | 1 Turret Gunner\n161\n0,058 FP/$\nVZUS OPOD\nRare Medium Data Runner\n3 Medium Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Medium Missile Bay\n139\n0,084 FP/$\nRAINBOW OM\nEpic Medium Freighter\n4 Medium Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Small Missile Bay\n129\n0,046 FP/$\nFIMBUL BYOS PACKLITE\nRare Medium Freighter\n2 Medium Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Medium Missile Bay\n104\n0,029 FP/$\nPEARCE X6\nRare Small Fighter\n4 Small Weapon Hardpoints | 4 X-Small Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Small Missile Bay | 1 Small Ammunition Module\n97.3\n0,105 FP/$\nFimbul BYOS Earp\nRare Small Fighter\n2 Medium Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Small Missile Bay\n90.5\n0,101 FP/$\nRAINBOW CHI\nEpic Small Fighter\n4 Small Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Small Missile Bay | 1 Small Ammunition Module\n78\n0,078 FP/$\nCALICO EVAC\nUncommon Medium Rescue\n2 Medium Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Small Missile Bay\n74.5\n0,029 FP/$\nBUSAN THRILL OF LIFE\nRare Small Fighter\n4 Small Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Small Missile Bay | 1 Small Ammunition Module\n69.8\n0,074 FP/$\nTUFA FEIST\nEpic Small Fighter\n3 Small Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Small Missile Bay\n60.9\n0,077 FP/$\nVZUS AMBWE\nRare Small Bounty Hunter\n2 Small Weapon Hardpoints | 2 X-Small Weapon Hardpoints | 1 Small Missile Bay\n54.3\n0,045 FP/$\nOGRIKA MIK\nRare Small Fighter\n3 Small Weapon Hardpoints | 1 X-Small Missile Bay | 1 Small Ammunition Module\n44.4\n0,058 FP/$\nPEARCE X5\nUncommon X-Small Fighter\n6 X-Small Weapon Hardpoints\n33.2\n0,236 FP/$\nPEARCE R6\nUncommon Small Repair\n2 Small Weapon Hardpoints | 1 X-Small Missile Bay\n31\n0,028 FP/$\nCALICO MEDTECH\nUncommon Small Rescue\n2 X-Small Weapon Hardpoints | 1 X-Small Missile Bay\n16.7\n0,018 FP/$\nOPAL JETJET\nUncommon X-Small Racer\n3 X-Small Weapon Hardpoints\n13.6\n0,044 FP/$\nPEARCE X4\nCommon Xx-Small Fighter\n4 Xx-Small Weapon Hardpoints\n9\n0,395 FP/$\nVZUS SOLOS\nCommon Xx-Small Racer\n2 Xx-Small Weapon Hardpoints | 2 Xxx-Small Weapon Hardpoints\n5.1\n0,180 FP/$\nFimbul ECOS Unibomba\nEpic Xx-Small Bomber\n2 Xx-Small Weapon Hardpoints\n4.1\n0,117 FP/$\nOPAL JET\nCommon Xx-Small Racer\n2 Xx-Small Weapon Hardpoints\n3.7\n0,183 FP/$\nFIMBUL AIRBIKE\nCommon Xx-Small Racer\n–\n0\n0,00 FP/$\nFIMBUL LOWBIE\nCommon X-Small Transport\n–\n0\n0,00 FP/$\nHow to read this table\nHow much firepower does a ship in Star Atlas bring to the table? And more important: How much stronger is that amount of firepower compared to other ships on the marketplace?\nA question that was difficult to answer until now, as there was no indication of the strength of the various components. This has changed with the recently published Sage Manual of the Star Atlas team.\nTalking to the developers we know that: “The components are not linearly additive. For example, two Small class maneuvering thrusters do not equate to a Medium size maneuvering thruster. The general rule of thumb is that component productivity increases by a factor of 2.47 with each class.”\nThe updated Firepower also takes into account the “Ship Make Bonuses” and “Ship Spec Bonuses” as we find them in the Sage Manual on page 29.\nBased on all currently available information, our Aephia experts have calculated the firepower of all ships from the Star Atlas Metaverse. There are a few points to keep in mind:\nWe currently do not know how much stronger a missile is compared to a Weapon Hardpoint. The current version assumes twice the firepower. This table will be updated as soon as we have new information.\nTurret Gunners may play in role how effectively a Weapon Hardpoint can be used, but have no effect on raw firepower for now.\nFirepower refers primarily to combat between ships. The Bomb Bay module is also currently not considered in the scoring, as we assume that bombs are primarily used against Star Bases or land-based facilities.\nThe same is true for the Drone Port Module. We know that there will be attack drones (like the X91) but can not estimate their firepower at this point.\nHaving an ammunition module equipped does not add to the firepower, but we still wanted to mention it in the notes for each ship.\nThe rating is of course not financial advice. It is speculative theorycrafting that has been developed by our most dedicated AEP members through extensive research and attention to detail.\nIn addition to pure firepower, we also calculated for each ship how much firepower you get for your money based on VWAP. To do this, we divide the firepower by the VWAP.",
